<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>SCSS on Refi Go</title><link>https://refigo.github.io/blog/tags/scss/</link><description>Recent content in SCSS on Refi Go</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 01:16:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://refigo.github.io/blog/tags/scss/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Hugo Stack 테마에서 코드 블록 자동 줄바꿈 활성화</title><link>https://refigo.github.io/blog/p/hugo-stack-%ED%85%8C%EB%A7%88%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9D-%EC%9E%90%EB%8F%99-%EC%A4%84%EB%B0%94%EA%BF%88-%ED%99%9C%EC%84%B1%ED%99%94/</link><pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 01:16:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://refigo.github.io/blog/p/hugo-stack-%ED%85%8C%EB%A7%88%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9D-%EC%9E%90%EB%8F%99-%EC%A4%84%EB%B0%94%EA%BF%88-%ED%99%9C%EC%84%B1%ED%99%94/</guid><description>&lt;p>Hugo 블로그의 Stack 테마를 사용할 때, 기본적으로 코드 블록이 wrapping되지 않는 문제가 있었다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="문제-상황">문제 상황
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://refigo.github.io/blog/p/hugo-stack-%ED%85%8C%EB%A7%88%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9D-%EC%9E%90%EB%8F%99-%EC%A4%84%EB%B0%94%EA%BF%88-%ED%99%9C%EC%84%B1%ED%99%94/non-wrapping-code-block.png"
width="1356"
